  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Use Phosphor icons or Lucide icons.",
    "Implement the site using raw Tailwind classes on semantic HTML elements. Use Shadcn sparingly (e.g. for contact form).",
    "Hero slider MUST have smooth fade transitions. The text MUST be overlaid cleanly (use bg-black/40 across the slider).",
    "Create dynamic pages (routing via react-router) for each Service and Package, rendering dummy SEO blog content and a contact form.",
    "Add 'data-testid' to ALL interactive elements.",
    "WhatsApp CTA must be fixed/floating on mobile, and clearly visible on desktop.",
    "Avoid Inter/Roboto. Use Cormorant Garamond for headings and Manrope for body text. Make sure to apply styling in .js files as frontend doesn't use typescript."
  ]
}